BENIN – A Volkswagen mechan­ic was on Wednesday shot dead in Benin City by some gun­men suspected to be members of a secret cult group. Daily Independent gath­ered that the gun-wielding men who stormed the me­chanic workshop at about 6 p.m. on Wednesday first shot sporadically into the air to scare residents before firing their target at close range. The deceased identified as Emmanuel Michael was at­tending to his customers in his mechanic workshop located at Osasogie Street, off Oguola/ Artilery Road in Benin City when the gunmen struck. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! Upon noticing that he was their target, the as­sailants immediately went straight to the said Emman­uel Michael and fired sever­al gunshots into his head, killing him on the spot. The gunmen were said to have later went berserk in the area as they engaged in a man­hunt for more people to kill. NDLEA Nabs 61 Suspected Drug Traffickers In Niger ACM Olagunju Advises Road Users, FRSC Officials To Avoid Last Minute Crashes The situation allegedly forced the residents to flee the area while owners of shops quickly locked up and fled. It took the intervention of the Edo State Joint Se­curity Team to restore nor­malcy in the area. Oguola, Eghosa and Osasogie streets were like ghost hunted areas when our correspondent visited while most vehicles coming to the area were diverted to avoid stray bullets. It was also discovered that more security officials have been drafted to the area to ensure peace. It would be recalled that a furniture maker was on Tuesday afternoon shot dead by some gunmen at Okabere Road in Upper Sakponba area of Benin City. The same Tuesday eve­ning, a middle-aged man was shot dead by some per­sons suspected to be mem­bers of a secret cult group in Aragua Street, off Wire Road in Benin City. The various killings sug­gest a renewed secret cult clash in Benin City, the Edo State capital. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION